Class IntList

java.lang.Object
  IntList

public class IntList
extends java.lang.Object

A naked recursive list of integers, similar to what we saw in lecture 3, but with a large number of additional methods.

Author:
P. N. Hilfinger, with some modifications by Josh Hug and melaniecebula [Do not modify this file.]
